metadata.name: Buff Jimmy #001
metadata.description: Introducing the "Buff Jimmy NFT" - the brawniest, most ripped amphibian in the digital realm! This hunky hoptastic collectible will make you jump for joy with its bulging biceps and muscular physique. Get ready to flex your NFT collection with this buff amphibious masterpiece that'll make other frog lovers green with envy. Ribbit your way to digital dominance and show the world that even frogs can hit the gym!
